text: Carlos Bienvenido Front Barrera (born 20 November 1980) is a Spanish rower. He competed in the men's eight event at the 1992 Summer Olympics as part of the Spanish team that finished 14th. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Spain Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Montsià Category:Catalan sportspeople
